    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Every plan ships the same substrate: 166 primitives, 14 themes, reproducible builds, multi-network publish, signed Merkle-chained audits, the Crucible captcha, Forge-auth, and bring-your-own LLM. What changes between plans is build-minute quota, storage, support latency, and access to the compliance-grade audit channel."
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "We never charge per page, per visitor, or per primitive. Page count and traffic are uncapped. If you outgrow Solo it is not because someone clicked your site — it is because your team is shipping more compute."
